The truth is exposed, and now the alternate Earth Katie may pay the price!! It's pure Vampblade on Vampblade madness!
Features 4 regular and risqué from Dan Mendoza (Zombie Tramp, DollFace) featuring some of Katie’s favorite video games. Covers are randomly distributed. Be sure to collect them all.
